Package com.btmatthews.maven.plugins.inmemdb.ldr.dbunit

This package contains the classes that implement the loaders for DBUnit data sets.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDBUnitLoader
    Abstract base class for loaders that use DBUnit to load data sets.
    DBUnitCSVLoader
    Loader that loads data from a DBUnit CSV data set.
    DBUnitFlatXMLLoader
    Loader that loads data from a DBUnit XML data set.
    DBUnitXLSLoader
    Loader that loads data from a DBUnit Excel data set.
    DBUnitXMLLoader
    Loader that loads data from a DBUnit XML data set.
